OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774699372
OL,3,CMaternity services at Royal
OL,4,CBournemouth Hospital require
OL,5,Cimprovement
OL,7,FAn inspection into the maternity
OL,8,Fservices at Royal Bournemouth Hospital
OL,9,Ffound there was "an increased risk
OL,10,Fthat women could be harmed".
OL,12,FThe inspection, carried out by the
OL,13,FCare Quality Commission (CQC) in
OL,14,FSeptember, was the first since the
OL,15,Fservice moved to its new location in
OL,16,Fthe Birth, Emergency, Critical Care
OL,17,Fand Child Health (BEACH) building, in
OL,18,FMarch 2025.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774699372
OL,3,CMaternity services at Royal
OL,4,CBournemouth Hospital require
OL,5,Cimprovement
OL,7,FMaternity services are now based at
OL,8,Fthe new purpose-built unit which
OL,9,Fprovides antenatal, triage, birth and
OL,10,Fpostnatal care.
OL,12,FThe CQC assessed how well the new unit
OL,13,Fwas functioning and whether it was
OL,14,Fkeeping women and babies safe, rating
OL,15,Fthe maternity services as requires
OL,16,Fimprovement.
OL,18,FWell-led and safe have been rated
OL,19,Frequires improvement and effective,
OL,20,Fcaring and responsive were rated as
OL,21,Fgood.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774699372
OL,3,CMaternity services at Royal
OL,4,CBournemouth Hospital require
OL,5,Cimprovement
OL,7,FThe report said "some aspects of the
OL,8,Fservice were not always safe and there
OL,9,Fwas limited assurance about safety".
OL,11,FIt added: "There was an increased risk
OL,12,Fthat women could be harmed."
OL,14,F"Delays could affect the safety of
OL,15,Fcare"
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774699372
OL,3,CMaternity services at Royal
OL,4,CBournemouth Hospital require
OL,5,Cimprovement
OL,7,FCatherine Campbell, CQC deputy
OL,8,Fdirector of hospitals, secondary and
OL,9,Fspecialist care for the South-West,
OL,10,Fsaid: "When we visited maternity
OL,11,Fservices at Royal Bournemouth
OL,12,FHospital, we found committed staff
OL,13,Fdoing their best in a busy new unit.
OL,15,F"But leaders didn't always have a
OL,16,Fclear understanding of the risks women
OL,17,Fwere facing, or the staffing pressures
OL,18,Fbuilding up across the service.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774699372
OL,3,CMaternity services at Royal
OL,4,CBournemouth Hospital require
OL,5,Cimprovement
OL,7,F"This meant women weren't always
OL,8,Ftriaged quickly, and delays could
OL,9,Faffect the safety of care.
OL,11,F"Women told us staff treated them with
OL,12,Fkindness and compassion, and we saw
OL,13,Fthis during our visit, but ongoing
OL,14,Fshortages, high sickness and gaps in
OL,15,Fthe rota made it harder for staff to
OL,16,Fgive people the timely support they
OL,17,Fneeded.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774699372
OL,3,CMaternity services at Royal
OL,4,CBournemouth Hospital require
OL,5,Cimprovement
OL,7,F"We also found the newborn security
OL,8,Fpolicy hadn't been updated for the new
OL,9,Fbuilding, and recovery bay CCTV
OL,10,Fcameras compromised women's privacy
OL,11,Fand dignity.
OL,13,F"The team acted promptly to remove the
OL,14,Fcameras and update the security
OL,15,Fpolicy, which was reassuring.
OL,17,F"However, there were strong areas of
OL,18,Fpractice too. Women felt involved in
OL,19,Fdecisions, enjoyed the privacy of
OL,20,Ftheir own rooms, and we saw midwives
OL,21,Fand doctors working well together.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774699372
OL,3,CMaternity services at Royal
OL,4,CBournemouth Hospital require
OL,5,Cimprovement
OL,7,F"CQC has set out the improvements the
OL,8,Fservice must make and has received
OL,9,Fimmediate assurances in several areas.
OL,11,F"Inspectors will keep the service
OL,12,Funder close review and reinspect to
OL,13,Fcheck progress."
OL,15,FThe inspection also found staff often
OL,16,Fdelayed the induction of labour
OL,17,Fprocess, leaving some women waiting
OL,18,Fmany hours or days and increasing
OL,19,Fdistress and the likelihood of
OL,20,Fintervention.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774699372
OL,3,CMaternity services at Royal
OL,4,CBournemouth Hospital require
OL,5,Cimprovement
OL,7,FStaffing shortages and limited theatre
OL,8,Fcapacity also led staff to cancel some
OL,9,Felective caesarean sections, creating
OL,10,Funcertainty and increasing anxiety for
OL,11,Fwomen.
OL,13,F"All women we spoke to were positive
OL,14,Fabout the service"
OL,16,FHowever, the report said: "The service
OL,17,Fhad a proactive and positive culture
OL,18,Fof safety, based on openness and
OL,19,Fhonesty.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774699372
OL,3,CMaternity services at Royal
OL,4,CBournemouth Hospital require
OL,5,Cimprovement
OL,7,F"They listened to concerns about
OL,8,Fsafety and investigated and reported
OL,9,Fsafety events.
OL,11,F"Lessons were learnt to continually
OL,12,Fidentify and embed good practice."
OL,14,FStaff were also described as
OL,15,Fprofessional, understanding and kind.
OL,17,FThe report said: "All women we spoke
OL,18,Fto were positive about the service.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774699372
OL,3,CMaternity services at Royal
OL,4,CBournemouth Hospital require
OL,5,Cimprovement
OL,7,F"Women told us they felt safe, well
OL,8,Fsupported and cared for by both the
OL,9,Fmidwifery and medical teams.
OL,11,F"Risks were explained by staff, and
OL,12,Fthey were involved in decision making."
OL,14,FThe service also had specialist
OL,15,Fmidwives to support vulnerable women
OL,16,Fand consultant obstetricians were
OL,17,Fpresent for difficult births.
OL,19,FThe Trust's response
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774699372
OL,3,CMaternity services at Royal
OL,4,CBournemouth Hospital require
OL,5,Cimprovement
OL,7,FUniversity Hospitals Dorset NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust, which runs the
OL,9,Fhospital, said: "This CQC report is
OL,10,Fpublished as our Maternity Team
OL,11,Fcelebrates a year in the BEACH
OL,12,FBuilding at RBH following the move
OL,13,Ffrom St Mary's in Poole.
OL,15,F"We made immediate improvements
OL,16,Ffollowing the CQC visit, including
OL,17,Fupdating our security policy.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774699372
OL,3,CMaternity services at Royal
OL,4,CBournemouth Hospital require
OL,5,Cimprovement
OL,7,F"Our Maternity Team has been
OL,8,Fcontinuing to identify better ways of
OL,9,Fworking in our new building to ensure
OL,10,Fwe provide safe and timely care.
OL,12,F"We are pleased that our service is
OL,13,Frated as good for being effective,
OL,14,Fcaring and responsive. Families
OL,15,Freported that our colleagues treated
OL,16,Fthem with kindness and compassion.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774699372
OL,3,CMaternity services at Royal
OL,4,CBournemouth Hospital require
OL,5,Cimprovement
OL,7,F"The CQC found that parents felt
OL,8,Finvolved in decisions and enjoyed the
OL,9,Fprivacy of their own rooms, with
OL,10,Fpartners now able to stay which was
OL,11,Fnot always possible at Poole Hospital.
OL,13,F"The CQC also reported that our
OL,14,Fmidwives and doctors worked well
OL,15,Ftogether.
OL,17,F"We look forward to welcoming the CQC
OL,18,Fback to check on progress following
OL,19,Ftheir inspection last September, as we
OL,20,Fcontinue to drive continuous
OL,21,Fimprovement across our services."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
